org.openstreetmap.gui.jmapviewer
Class GPSInfo

java.lang.Object
  org.openstreetmap.gui.jmapviewer.GPSInfo

public class GPSInfo
extends Object

Class to handle info from the GPS. Use: make instances of this class see http://www.gpsinformation.org/dale/nmea.htm for information about tags

Author:
Johan and Sebastian
